descriptions.value:
This Music Kit will replace all of the music in the game and is shareable with anyone you are playing with. It also includes an MVP Anthem that plays for everyone in the match when you are MVP.

The Music Kit replaces the following music:
- Main Menu
- Round Start and End
- Map Objective
- Ten Second Warning
- Death Camera
Mixing pulsating strings and synths with pounding war drums, prepare yourself for battle with this thunderous soundtrack from composer Ian Hultquist.
